events.text: Welcome to your new league!
The Gold Rush traded Mike Gordon and a 2020 1st round pick (SAC) to the Whalers for Andre Eakins.
The High traded Roy Jones to the Vultures for Albert Vazquez, a 2020 1st round pick (PHO), a 2021 2nd round pick (PHO), and a 2023 1st round pick (PHO).
The Gold Rush traded Chris Brown, Shawn Malone, and a 2022 1st round pick (SAC) to the Riots for Matt Allen.
The Bankers traded Lawrence Mills, Robert Nixon, and Ryan Brickley to the Whalers for Mike Williams, Anthony Paulos, Stefan Pantic, and a 2020 1st round pick (SAC).
The Massacre traded Bison Purnell to the Roses for Terrence Primus, Shamar Harris, a 2020 1st round pick (POR), and a 2020 2nd round pick (POR).

The Beavers traded Aubrey Friday and Matt Edney to the Gold Rush for Jamel Harris, Grigoriy Karasev, Mael Hangoue, Chad Lofton, D.J. Hatch, a 2021 2nd round pick (SAC), and a 2023 2nd round pick (SAC).
